t: "And when the devil decorated/beautified for them their works/deeds , and he said: \"No defeater/conqueror from the people for you today and that I am a savior/rescuer for you.\" So when the two groups saw each other, he returned/withdrew on his two heels, and he said: \"That I am innocent/renouncing/separating from you, that I, I see/understand what you do not see/understand, that I, I fear God, and God (is) strong (severe) in the punishment"